{"tid":1591442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[荃灣浮屍] 五月天母親區議員衝出黎抽水","createTime":"2019-09-24T07:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T08:22:49.000Z","uid":79016,"like":83,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"9900a858eda14fb071925c9eab1532c0a7e8801c","tid":1591442,"uid":79016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6HKDmka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6HKDmka.jpg&h=202ab013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢叫鄒秉恬<br />\n人稱海濱土皇帝<br />\n係荃灣海濱選區區議員<br />\n佢居位海濱皇位超過20年<br />\n經常自稱實幹實績不取巧<br />\n<br />\n事沿今朝荃灣發現浮屍<br />\n呢位鄒議員衝出黎叫人路過要合十<br />\n強調自己<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">實幹實績緊貼時事又一例證</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEra3zp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEra3zp.jpg&h=15ed1d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢唯一賣點係獨立議員<br />\n冇任何政治聯絡<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QrgFGoK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQrgFGoK.jpg&h=dc6e8dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rCfWeJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrCfWeJM.jpg&h=06f8ae8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你睇下佢<br />\n佢會去遊行拍片公開反送中<br />\n又會到連農牆支持<br />\n又會屌林莫<br />\n但從來冇關心新屋嶺冇關心8.31 等等<br />\n甚至唔會了解呢期死者係咪被自殺<br />\n直至今日終於係自己選區發生又一單<br />\n佢衝出黎讚揚自己會緊貼時事做實事<br />\n用個唔適合嘅emoji<br />\n明顯係抽死者水極不尊重死者同家屬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O6xJxrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO6xJxrp.jpg&h=6435cce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢做鳩野唔係冇前科<br />\n先係曲線禁止女性係沙灘著三點式<br />\n近期又叫居民食屎<br />\n這是正式錄用的區議員嗎？<br />\n<br />\n佢有搞五月天<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">母親</span>演唱會<br />\n要門票可以揾佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a2b1ac0bbd2480cf7e2e96a41699b009f7cd66","tid":1591442,"uid":169079,"like":18,